freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Continued cold symptoms with coughing , congestion, and fatigue. No fever and oxygen above 94 sat, which is normal for me. Probably unrelated to the vaccine.
Coughing, productive cough, nausea, vomiting, poor appetite, headache, fatigue, no fever.  I was told that I could have COVID but the Covid test was negative.
Seems like a common cold with post nasal drip and cough. No fever or other symptoms. My one year old grandson had the same and I watched him.
